<div class="content" style="color: #3e3a39"> 
<p>親愛的 <%=@order.product_boxing.product.company.user.last_name%> <%=@order.product_boxing.product.company.user.first_name%>，您好！</p>	
<p>您有一筆新的出貨，出貨編號：<%=@order.id %></p>
<p>以下是出貨明細：</p>
<table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 0 auto;">
	<tr>
		<th style="min-width: 60px;">出貨編號</th>
		<th style="min-width: 75px;">品項</th>
		<th style="min-width: 60px;">出貨數量</th>
		<th style="min-width: 40px;">金額</th>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td><%= @order.id %></td>	
		<td>
			<%if @order.product_boxing.product.product_images.first %>
				<div class="text-center">
					<%= image_tag @order.product_boxing.product.cover.url(:medium), style: 'width: 40px; height: 40px;' %>			
			    </div>
			<%end%> 	
	    	<div class="text-center"><%= @order.product_boxing.product.name%></div>   			
		</td>	
		<td><%= @order.quantity %>箱 (<%="%g" % @order.product_boxing.quantity%><%= Hash[unitOptions].rassoc(@order.product_boxing.product.unit).first %>/箱)</td>	
		<td><%= @order.price.to_i+ @order.shipping_rates.to_i %>元</td>	
	</tr>		
</table>
<br>
<br>
<div style="text-align:center; font-size: 15px;">
	<%=link_to '進入後台處理此出貨', Rails.configuration.smallfarmer01_host+'/orders/index?called_smallfarmer_c=false', style: 'padding: 10px 8px; color: #ffffff; background: #DE562C; box-shadow: 3px 3px rgb(209, 209, 200); text-decoration: none;'%>
</div>	
</div>